1 tomato
1 cucumber
1 carrot
1 packet hummus
6 Mini Flour Tortillas
1 bag salad leaves
1 packet Shredded Cheddar Cheese

Thinly slice tomato into half-moons. Thinly slice cucumber into batons. Grate carrot.

Spread some hummus over mini flour tortillas. Divide carrot, tomato, cucumber and salad leaves between tortillas. Sprinkle with shredded Cheddar cheese.

Tuck in ends of tortillas and roll into wraps. Wrap in foil or plastic wrap. Refrigerate until ready to serve.